::DrillBit::

DrillBit had enough, of what he was hearing.
"Shut up! KitKat is in Command, untill she gives that to another." He
picked KitKat up, and began walking off. 
"Fine, go Terrorsaur. We are getting to that cave for cover, now Atma,
how do we get there? We'll have to forget about searching the base
ruins."
